22:09.412 --> 22:10.844
[GRUNTING]

22:19.356 --> 22:20.522
Wait, wait, wait, wait.

22:20.525 --> 22:22.556
Hey. The streets are talking, man.

22:22.558 --> 22:23.976
I heard what you did to Block.

22:23.979 --> 22:25.045
What'd you hear?

22:25.048 --> 22:27.428
I heard you lit his ass up.

22:27.431 --> 22:30.431
Good, that should save us some time.

22:30.433 --> 22:32.038
Tell me about Green Light.

22:32.041 --> 22:34.969
I know your MO After I tell
you what you wanna know,

22:34.971 --> 22:37.171
you just gonna knock me
out and call the cops,

22:37.173 --> 22:38.806
and that'll be my third strike.

22:38.808 --> 22:40.341
I get 30 years, man.

22:40.343 --> 22:42.823
Really should've thought about
that before you started dealing.

22:42.826 --> 22:44.678
