22:44.680 --> 22:45.991
You deserve something.

22:45.994 --> 22:48.482
Okay. But 30 years?
I mean, come on, man.

22:48.484 --> 22:51.485
They throwing brothers in jail
forever, like it ain't nothing.

22:52.788 --> 22:54.221
All right.

22:54.223 --> 22:57.725
I won't call the cops if you
tell me what I need to know,

22:57.728 --> 23:00.822
and you stop selling drugs.

23:01.998 --> 23:04.198
Now, I hear you dealing again,

23:05.175 --> 23:06.702
I'mma come find you.

23:06.705 --> 23:08.772
Okay. Deal.

23:08.775 --> 23:10.904
So I leave the money at the drop spot.

23:10.906 --> 23:12.640
I go pick up the product at a warehouse

23:12.642 --> 23:14.742
on 389 Hart Avenue.

23:14.744 --> 23:16.577
Re-up is every Thursday at noon.

23:16.579 --> 23:19.513
Hey, hey, real, real quick.
Before you knock me out,

23:19.515 --> 23:21.150
uh, you think I can get a pic?

23:22.584 --> 23:24.784
