23:51.754 --> 23:54.096
- Yeah, I've been official.
- [CHUCKLES]

23:54.099 --> 23:55.499
You just didn't notice it.

23:55.502 --> 23:57.702
Okay, so what you gonna do?

23:58.784 --> 24:01.218
I don't want people to see me like this.

24:01.221 --> 24:03.731
I don't know. I mean, what do you think?

24:04.774 --> 24:08.810
Um, I think you've been through a lot.

24:11.975 --> 24:15.903
[CLEARS THROAT] So, I quit the track team.

24:17.347 --> 24:19.013
- What? For real?
- Mmm-hmm.

24:20.984 --> 24:22.283
Huh.

24:23.219 --> 24:25.419
[COMMENTATOR SPEAKING
INDISTINCTLY ON TV]

24:29.448 --> 24:30.848
You know what?

24:31.761 --> 24:33.194
I'mma do it.

24:34.103 --> 24:36.207
Yeah. People should see that it takes

24:36.210 --> 24:38.202
