34:01.196 --> 34:03.630
they'd probably take him out for you.

34:03.633 --> 34:07.333
The people in Freeland love that boy,

34:07.336 --> 34:10.603
and he has every reason
to hate Black Lightning.

34:10.605 --> 34:14.341
He doesn't know it yet, but he does.

34:14.342 --> 34:20.413
Maybe you can help him realize just
how much he hates Black Lightning.

34:32.127 --> 34:35.056
Hey! What you doing here so early?

34:35.060 --> 34:38.130
Um, your mom asked my dad to come by,

34:38.141 --> 34:40.857
