34:40.860 --> 34:42.900
Yo, where'd all this stuff come from?

34:42.904 --> 34:44.536
Anonymous donor.

34:44.539 --> 34:47.107
Yeah, whoever it is,
they're hooking it up.

34:47.109 --> 34:48.908
