care of my medical bills,

34:48.909 --> 34:50.935
and helping my mom out with rent.

35:03.025 --> 35:04.692
Principal Pierce.

35:07.933 --> 35:09.403
Hey, Khalil.

35:11.233 --> 35:12.899
