36:12.861 --> 36:14.894
along with each board member.

36:16.264 --> 36:17.721
I don't like it.

36:17.724 --> 36:21.267
You can either save Bernard,
or you can retain final say,

36:21.269 --> 36:23.903
but they're not gonna
let you have both. So...

36:31.845 --> 36:33.349
Tell them I'll do it.

36:33.352 --> 36:35.915
- Okay, I'll let them know.
- Thank you.

36:39.488 --> 36:40.820
[DOOR CLOSES]

