36:56.805 --> 36:59.864
This Khalil situation is bothering me.

37:01.142 --> 37:02.809
He's never gonna walk again.

37:02.811 --> 37:05.111
Yeah, I know. I'm up to
speed. Jennifer told me.

37:05.113 --> 37:06.379
<i>Hey, I don't know, Lynn.</i>

37:06.381 --> 37:11.217
LaWanda, Khalil,
Reverend Holt, Bernard...

37:12.621 --> 37:16.122
I just used to be able to handle
the collateral damage a lot better.

37:16.124 --> 37:17.395
[SIGHS]

37:17.398 --> 37:18.964
Jefferson, I'm really busy right now.

37:18.967 --> 37:20.433
Can we talk about this later?

37:23.231 --> 37:25.632
Yeah. Yeah, sure, um...

37:25.635 --> 37:27.602
I'll call you later.

37:34.910 --> 37:36.731
