sorry to bother you,

37:48.039 --> 37:49.661
but I didn't know who else to call.

37:49.664 --> 37:51.853
Bernard went to a dope
house looking for drugs.

37:51.856 --> 37:54.275
Wait, what? Okay, slow
down. What, what happened?

37:54.278 --> 37:57.730
After our meeting, Bernard wouldn't
stop talking about Green Light.

37:57.732 --> 38:01.000
- What's the address?
- 367, 34th Street.

38:01.002 --> 38:03.703
I went there to get him, but
some of The Hundred came out.

38:03.705 --> 38:06.306
They pistol-whipped me.
The cops didn't do nothing.

38:06.308 --> 38:07.807
<i>Okay, I'll make some calls.</i>

