39:11.828 --> 39:14.373
<i>♪ To help the needy
And guard the blinded ♪</i>

39:14.376 --> 39:16.939
<i>♪ Last night I saw a
superhero He was black ♪</i>

39:16.942 --> 39:19.812
<i>♪ He said This is for the
street Black Lightning's back ♪</i>

39:19.814 --> 39:22.528
I don't understand how
he got hooked so quick.

39:24.129 --> 39:26.396
This new drug is bad like that.

39:26.399 --> 39:29.935
But Bernard is in the best
treatment facility in Freeland,

39:29.938 --> 39:34.130
and when he's straight, we'll get
him back on track and into college.

39:34.133 --> 39:37.700
I've put everything I had
