39:37.703 --> 39:39.169
I...

39:48.009 --> 39:49.799
I appreciate everything
you've done for us.

39:49.802 --> 39:51.210
Oh, of course. Of course.

39:52.547 --> 39:53.579
Thank you.

39:53.581 --> 39:55.599
Hmm. Stay in touch.

