40:14.441 --> 40:19.978
[LYNN] <i>Hi, Jefferson, it's me.</i>
<i>I'm sorry about earlier today.</i>

40:19.981 --> 40:23.111
<i>All I can say is, this Black Lightning</i>

40:23.114 --> 40:26.395
<i>stuff has my emotions all over the place.</i>

40:26.398 --> 40:29.449
<i>If I'm being honest, I'm angry with you.</i>

40:29.451 --> 40:31.851
<i>But that doesn't mean, I don't love you.</i>

40:31.854 --> 40:34.227
How'd you like the gifts?

40:35.590 --> 40:38.033
[PANTS]

40:38.036 --> 40:41.094
You mind keeping the lights
